# ------------------------------------------------------------------
# 1️⃣  Rust build artifacts (the `target/` folder)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------
# Ignore the entire `target` directory for every crate in the repo.
# If you really only want to hide the `debug` sub‑folder, replace
# the next line with `target/debug/` instead.
target/

# ------------------------------------------------------------------
# 2️⃣  Individual debug folders (optional, if you prefer)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------
# target/debug/        # <- hides `debug` in every `target/` tree
# target/release/      # <- hides `release` too, if you wish
# ------------------------------------------------------------------
# 3️⃣  Miscellaneous useful ignores
# ------------------------------------------------------------------
# Cargo.lock is kept in the workspace root, but if you have
# separate crates you can ignore them in each crate.
# (Leave it commented out if you want the lock file tracked.)
Cargo.lock

